Effect.en:
2 Effect Monsters
During your Main Phase: You can Fusion Summon 1 Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, using monsters you control as Fusion Material. If a Fusion Monster is Fusion Summoned to a zone this card points to: You can Special Summon 1 monster with 1000 or less ATK from your hand. You can only use each effect of "Proxy F Magician" once per turn.
